graph LR
    NotebookController[Notebook Controller]

    %% External Dependencies
    NotebookController -->|platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes v1.22.0+]
    NotebookController -->|framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.21.0]
    NotebookController -.->|optional ingress| Istio[Istio v1.x]
    NotebookController -.->|optional metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus v2.x]
    NotebookController -.->|optional auth proxy| KubeRBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    NotebookController -->|CRD extension| ODHNotebookController[odh-notebook-controller]
    NotebookController <-->|creates CRs| JupyterWebApp[jupyter-web-app]
    NotebookController <-->|status monitoring| ODHDashboard[odh-dashboard]
    NotebookController -->|container images| NotebookImages[notebook-images]

    %% API Server (central hub)
    Kubernetes -->|API Server| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    NotebookController -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI

    %% Integration Points
    JupyterWebApp -->|creates Notebook CRs| K8sAPI
    ODHDashboard -->|reads Notebook status| K8sAPI
    Prometheus -.->|scrapes /metrics| NotebookController
    Istio -.->|VirtualService routing| NotebookController

    %% Managed Resources
    NotebookController -->|creates/manages| StatefulSets[StatefulSets]
    NotebookController -->|creates/manages| Services[Services]
    NotebookController -.->|creates when USE_ISTIO=true| VirtualServices[Istio VirtualServices]

    %% CRDs
    NotebookController -->|watches/manages| NotebookCRD[Notebook CRD<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]

    %% Culling integration
    NotebookController -->|polls /api/kernels| NotebookPods[Notebook Pods<br/>8888/TCP]

    %% Styling
    style NotebookController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    style Kubernetes fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#fff
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#fff
    style KubeRBACProxy fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#fff

    style ODHNotebookController fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style JupyterWebApp fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ODHDashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style NotebookImages fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style StatefulSets fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Services fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style VirtualServices fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#fff
